text: Houses in Astcote Astcote is a hamlet in near the town of Towcester in Northamptonshire, England. It is in the civil parish of Pattishall . The settlement was recorded in the Domesday Book under the name of Aviescote. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Hamlets in Northamptonshire Category:South Northamptonshire District
